{"TopicId":178713,"ForumId":39,"TopicTitle":"Should we create a KerbalGeoFiction site?","CreatedByName":"MedwedianPresident","CreatedById":12212,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-10-03T18:56:38Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"MedwedianPresident","CreatedById":12212,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-10-03T18:56:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere is an interesting website called \u003Ca href=\u0022https://opengeofiction.net/\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EOpenGeoFiction\u003C/a\u003E where contributors can create fictional countries within a world that uses the OpenStreetMap framework. This results in a giant map with lots of lore and documentation.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI wonder if something like this could be done for Kerbin. The main problems would be:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\na.) setting up the respective OSM server,\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nb.) importing at least the major coastlines of Kerbin into the map and\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nc.) determining to which extent terrain can be fictionalized.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf done correctly, a successful Kerbal Geofiction project would open up a whole new dimension for the forum community to cooperate.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat do you think?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kerbalstar","CreatedById":154159,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-10-03T19:50:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLooking at the OGF website, this could be interesting. How would one do it?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"RealKerbal3x","CreatedById":183830,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-10-03T19:55:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSounds interesting, but I reckon quite a few on here (including me)\u00A0envisage a united Kerbin society\u00A0with no countries. I\u2019m not sure how that would work on there.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222018-10-03T19:55:28Z\u0022 title=\u002210/03/2018 07:55  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00225 yr\u0022\u003EOctober 3, 2018\u003C/time\u003E by RealKerbal3x\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MedwedianPresident","CreatedById":12212,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-10-03T19:55:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223461705\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022178713\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221538596250\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022154159\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022kerbalstar\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 minutes ago, kerbalstar said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLooking at the OGF website, this could be interesting. How would one do it?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n1. \u003Ca href=\u0022https://switch2osm.org/manually-building-a-tile-server-16-04-2-lts/\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003ECreate a OSM tile server\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n2. Extract a basic heightmap (e.g. just the coastlines) - this should be doable. Import it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n3. Add the most important features manually.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n4. Begin fictionalizing and detailing the terrain (e.g. adding countries, cities, fields, space centers, roads, railways, etc...).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kerbalstar","CreatedById":154159,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-10-03T22:09:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223461707\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022178713\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221538596549\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002212212\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022MedwedianPresident\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, MedwedianPresident said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n1. \u003Ca href=\u0022https://switch2osm.org/manually-building-a-tile-server-16-04-2-lts/\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003ECreate a OSM tile server\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n2. Extract a basic heightmap (e.g. just the coastlines) - this should be doable. Import it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n3. Add the most important features manually.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n4. Begin fictionalizing and detailing the terrain (e.g. adding countries, cities, fields, space centers, roads, railways, etc...).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOkay. If some one else would agree to\u00A0help, that would be great!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"linuxgurugamer","CreatedById":129964,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-10-03T22:14:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou should get permission from Squad before doing this.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kerbalstar","CreatedById":154159,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-10-03T23:33:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223461767\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022178713\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221538604846\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022129964\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022linuxgurugamer\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, linuxgurugamer said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou should get permission from Squad before doing this.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI strongly agree!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Ultimate Steve","CreatedById":161505,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-10-04T00:45:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223461767\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022178713\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221538604846\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022129964\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022linuxgurugamer\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, linuxgurugamer said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou should get permission from Squad before doing this.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSQUAD is not who we should ask any more, I think.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"linuxgurugamer","CreatedById":129964,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-10-04T01:28:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223461821\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022178713\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221538613908\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022161505\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Ultimate Steve\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n43 minutes ago, Ultimate Steve said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSQUAD is not who we should ask any more, I think.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSquad will pass it up the line to Take-2, if they can\u0027t make the decision themselves\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MedwedianPresident","CreatedById":12212,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-10-04T11:55:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223461833\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022178713\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221538616513\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022129964\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022linuxgurugamer\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n10 hours ago, linuxgurugamer said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSquad will pass it up the line to Take-2, if they can\u0027t make the decision themselves\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u2019m sure that they will not prohibit this as long as the site stays non-commercial and we will only use the coastlines of Kerbin.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"linuxgurugamer","CreatedById":129964,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-10-04T12:58:37Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223462017\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022178713\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221538654129\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002212212\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022MedwedianPresident\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, MedwedianPresident said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u2019m sure that they will not prohibit this as long as the site stays non-commercial and we will only use the coastlines of Kerbin.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThen why not ask?\u00A0 If you don\u0027t, you are only asking for trouble down the road, if you ask, then you know up front.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere have been lots of cases where fan sites have been shut down by the copyright owners for various reasons.\u00A0 Best to get it cleared up front first.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MedwedianPresident","CreatedById":12212,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-10-04T13:07:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223462042\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022178713\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221538657917\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022129964\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022linuxgurugamer\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n9 minutes ago, linuxgurugamer said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThen why not ask?\u00A0 If you don\u0027t, you are only asking for trouble down the road, if you ask, then you know up front.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere have been lots of cases where fan sites have been shut down by the copyright owners for various reasons.\u00A0 Best to get it cleared up front first.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI am not saying \u0022let\u0027s not ask\u0022, just saying \u0022as\u00A0 long as we ask for permission, they will surely say yes\u0022.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"FleshJeb","CreatedById":111640,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-10-04T18:12:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI think it\u0027s an interesting idea, but be aware of Guideline 2.2j - No roleplaying on THIS forum\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/guidelines/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003Ehttps://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/guidelines/\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRationale:\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/132441-whats-the-story-behind-the-roleplay-guideline/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003Ehttps://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/132441-whats-the-story-behind-the-roleplay-guideline/\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNote: I am\u00A0NOT a moderator, just seeking to inform.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MedwedianPresident","CreatedById":12212,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-10-05T08:46:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223462210\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022178713\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221538676725\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022111640\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022FleshJeb\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n14 hours ago, FleshJeb said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI think it\u0027s an interesting idea, but be aware of Guideline 2.2j - No roleplaying on THIS forum\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/guidelines/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003Ehttps://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/guidelines/\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRationale:\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/132441-whats-the-story-behind-the-roleplay-guideline/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003Ehttps://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/132441-whats-the-story-behind-the-roleplay-guideline/\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNote: I am\u00A0NOT a moderator, just seeking to inform.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe RP rule can be avoided by transferring the forum to the website and/or working on a discord server. Just the most important results and achievements will be presented here.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"linuxgurugamer","CreatedById":129964,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-10-05T12:30:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe RP rule can be avoided by posting the results and achievements in the third person (usually)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nnote:\u00A0 I am not a moderator, just answering from experience\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-10-05T19:45:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis work of fans has been moved to Fan Works.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd yes, any actual roleplaying would need to take place away from our forum.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAs for permission to use things Squad made, \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/149302-darth-badie/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022149302\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/149302-darth-badie/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Darth Badie\u003C/a\u003E would be the one to ask.\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MedwedianPresident","CreatedById":12212,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-10-06T09:31:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223462777\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022178713\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221538768753\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002227914\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Vanamonde\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n13 hours ago, Vanamonde said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis work of fans has been moved to Fan Works.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd yes, any actual roleplaying would need to take place away from our forum.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAs for permission to use things Squad made, \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/149302-darth-badie/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022149302\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/149302-darth-badie/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Darth Badie\u003C/a\u003E would be the one to ask.\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThank you, I have composed and sent a \u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/149302-darth-badie/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003Emessage\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0to him.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222018-10-06T09:38:54Z\u0022 title=\u002210/06/2018 09:38  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00225 yr\u0022\u003EOctober 6, 2018\u003C/time\u003E by MedwedianPresident\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"orl0pl","CreatedById":228978,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-06-20T05:45:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs there any progress?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Royalswissarmyknife","CreatedById":216092,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-06-20T21:37:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nim guessing no as the last post was from 4-5 years ago\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}